jc.dotplot <- function(x) {
  # x is HLE or LE in c()　vector
  names(x)<-Wakayama::pref$pref.J
  x<-x[order(x)]

}

colfunc <- colorRampPalette(c("gray90","black"))

par(family= "HiraKakuProN-W3")

dotchart(
  main = "平均寿命(2015年, 男性)",
  jc.dotplot(d_m$LE_2015),
  cex = 0.7,
  lcolor = "gray90",
  pch = 19,
  col = colfunc(47),
  pt.cex = 1.5
)

abline(v = 79, lty = 2)
